Peter, a legend half British and half Kiwi. 
All this guy does is epic, 
He's a master builder and love the burningmans kind of festivals.
Every meal with him is an unforgettable fancy experience. He get out from his tiny car colourful lights, all the kind of decorations, cutlery set up for 20 people and delicious food. Great speaker, he make friends everywhere he goes, we had some crazy moments with random people that were joining our festss on the side of the roads.
Constantly on the flow, great songwriter and friend.
Its always good time for a cup of tee when he's around. 
Has been a delight spending time with him. Found in him a brother  and going to join him in some burnings soon both in Australia and NZ! Forever greateful also for having just build me the kitchen of my van!

This Angel here is Rebecca. 
We met during her last week of the Australian trip and shared so much love, blissfull healings and crazy moments together in so tiny time. 
Forever glad for it!
She has an incredible voice and a powerful smile. We played and sang in so many different places, touching the soul of the people all the time. 
In the video she's smashing and burning the guitar that has travelled with her during the last year, letting go of all the emotions that doesnt serve anymore. Infinite Loveeee ‚ù§
Had a cup of tee with this beautiful Lady in her house in the middle of  the rain forest during sunset time! What a view and what a nice piece of memory ! Thank you ‚ù§
